verbose_text: Further, levodopa, a precursor to dopamine that is commonly used to treat Parkinson 's disease (PD), restores timing performance in rats with lesions to the SNc but not in those with lesions to the CPu, which may reflect the distinct roles of these structures in temporal calculation.
